    <lb n="9"/>ταῦτα <choice><corr>γίνεται</corr><sic>γε<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ι</supplied>νετε</sic></choice>. καὶ ἡ μήτηρ μου εἶπε Ἀ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ρ</unclear>-

