    <lb n="13"/>τῇ ἡμέρᾳ <num value="12">ιβ</num> ὅτι <choice><corr>ἔπλευσας</corr><sic>επλευσες</sic></choice>. <app type="editorial"><lem><choice><corr>λοιπὸν</corr><sic>λυπον</sic></choice></lem><rdg><choice><corr>λύραν</corr><sic>λυρον</sic></choice></rdg></app> πέμψον εἴ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ς</supplied> 

